@host = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### GET TODAS SOLICITAÇÕES DE RECURSOS
GET {{host}}/allocation-requests
Accept: application/json

### GET SOLICITAÇÃO DE RECURSO ESPECÍFICO
GET {{host}}/allocation-requests/3
Accept: application/json

### GET TODOS AS POSIÇÕES
GET {{host}}/positions
Accept: application/json

### NOVA SOLICITAÇÃO DE RECURSO
POST {{host}}/allocation-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "startDate": "01/10/2025",
    "endDate": "31/10/2025",
    "dailyHours": 12,
    "priority": "HIGH",
    "positionId": 2,
    "projectId": 1
}

### EDITAR SOLICITAÇÃO DE RECURSO
PUT {{host}}/allocation-requests/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "startDate": "31/12/2024",
    "endDate": "03/04/2027",
    "dailyHours": 2,
    "priority": "MEDIUM",
    "positionId": 1
}

### DESABILITAR RECURSO
DELETE {{host}}/allocation-requests/2
Content-Type: application/json

### DELETAR RECURSO
DELETE {{host}}/allocation-requests/1/hard-delete
Content-Type: application/json